OL,3,C'It's devastating': Villagers issue
OL,4,Cplea for return of 'stolen' goose
OL,6,FFeathers have been ruffled in a Kent
OL,7,Fvillage after a goose nicknamed
OL,8,FGandalf was allegedly stolen in broad
OL,9,Fdaylight, leaving behind his companion
OL,10,F'Ryan Gosling'.
OL,12,FA witness reportedly saw a driver
OL,13,Fbundle the goose into the back of a
OL,14,Fblack estate car, prompting fury from
OL,15,Fthe local community.
OL,17,FFor two years the birds, Ryan and
OL,18,FGandalf, have been living on Basted
OL,19,FMillpond, near Borough Green.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
