CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779210357
OL,3,C'It's devastating': Villagers issue
OL,4,Cplea for return of 'stolen' goose
OL,6,FBut last week a passer by claimed to
OL,7,Fhave seen a motorist snatch the bird
OL,8,Fand drive away.
OL,10,FA resident from a nearby village, Jane
OL,11,FSewell-Watts, said she was shocked
OL,12,Fanyone would do this to a bird.
OL,14,FShe said: "It's a community area,
OL,15,Fpeople enjoy local wildlife. You know
OL,16,Fthe geese have been there regularly.
OL,18,F"They have provided a lot of happiness
OL,19,Fto people with their mental health and
OL,20,Fnow this. It's devastating."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
