FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779210357
OL,3,C'It's devastating': Villagers issue
OL,4,Cplea for return of 'stolen' goose
OL,6,FMs Sewell-Watts hopes the bird is
OL,7,Funharmed and has begged the thieves to
OL,8,Freturn it.
OL,10,FBenjamin McConnachie, landlord of The
OL,11,FPlough at Basted, is offering a #400
OL,12,Freward for information leading to the
OL,13,Fconviction of the "low-lifes" alleged
OL,14,Fto have stolen the bird.
OL,16,FHe said: "People are so upset, kids,
OL,17,Fmothers, grandparents.
OL,19,F"The way we look at it, it was their
OL,20,Fpond, they were residents, it was
OL,21,Ftheir pond, that was their home."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
