PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779210357
OL,3,C'It's devastating': Villagers issue
OL,4,Cplea for return of 'stolen' goose
OL,6,F"We've actually now set up a group, a
OL,7,Ftrust fund to protect the geese."
OL,9,FIt's thought that Gandalf may
OL,10,Foriginally have been released by
OL,11,Fsomeone who could no longer look after
OL,12,Fhim, and a couple from nearby bought
OL,13,Fhim Ryan as a companion.
OL,15,FGeese are sociable animals and the
OL,16,Fconcerned residents have since
OL,17,Ftravelled some distance to purchase a
OL,18,Fnew companion for the remaining bird -
OL,19,Falready nicknamed - 'Gengoose Khan'.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
