OL,3,C'It's devastating': Villagers issue
OL,4,Cplea for return of 'stolen' goose
OL,6,FA spokesman for Kent Police said:
OL,7,F"Inquiries are under way to establish
OL,8,Fthe circumstances in line with
OL,9,Foffences under the Wildlife and
OL,10,FCountryside Act 1981."
